1. install the packages as devDependency - 
    - gulp
    - gulp-rename
    - gulp-uglify

    -> npm i -dev gulp gulp-rename gulp-uglify

2. Place all your scripts inside the src folder.


3. Then create a gulpfile.js file and create the minifyJS() function and default export it.

4. Then Run this command "npx gulp" to start the minification process
